  25:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
  26:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****                         ##### FMC peripheral features #####
  27:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
  28:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   [..] The Flexible memory controller (FMC) includes following memory controllers:
  29:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        (+) The NOR/PSRAM memory controller
  30:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****      (+) The NAND memory controller
ARM GAS  C:\Users\28576\AppData\Local\Temp\ccYw9wfC.s 			page 2


  31:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        (+) The Synchronous DRAM (SDRAM) controller
  32:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c **** 
  33:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   [..] The FMC functional block makes the interface with synchronous and asynchronous static
  34:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        memories and SDRAM memories. Its main purposes are:
  35:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        (+) to translate AHB transactions into the appropriate external device protocol
  36:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        (+) to meet the access time requirements of the external memory devices
  37:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c **** 
  38:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   [..] All external memories share the addresses, data and control signals with the controller.
  39:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        Each external device is accessed by means of a unique Chip Select. The FMC performs
  40:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        only one access at a time to an external device.
  41:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****        The main features of the FMC controller are the following:
  42:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****         (+) Interface with static-memory mapped devices including:
  43:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****            (++) Static random access memory (SRAM)
  44:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****            (++) Read-only memory (ROM)
  45:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****            (++) NOR Flash memory/OneNAND Flash memory
  46:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****            (++) PSRAM (4 memory banks)
  47:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****            (++) Two banks of NAND Flash memory with ECC hardware to check up to 8 Kbytes of
  48:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****                 data
  49:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****         (+) Interface with synchronous DRAM (SDRAM) memories
  50:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****         (+) Independent Chip Select control for each memory bank
  51:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****         (+) Independent configuration for each memory bank
  52:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c **** 
  53:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   @endverbatim
  54:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_ll_fmc.c ****   ******************************************************************************
